  "detailed_description": "<strong>Cubik</strong> is a minimalist puzzle game revolving around cubes. Each cube can be rotated vertically or horizontally. The goal of the game is to match all cube color with the background.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/0e91e4eee462fa3bb9a314cce51071ef.poster.avif?t=1724771899\" width=500 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/0e91e4eee462fa3bb9a314cce51071ef.webm?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/0e91e4eee462fa3bb9a314cce51071ef.mp4?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When holding the cube, four wings will appear indicating the color of the unseen four faces. When dragging, one wing will appear indicating the color of the upcoming face.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/8a08b7c75727f6b77f79f06f2b8566b8.poster.avif?t=1724771899\" width=500 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/8a08b7c75727f6b77f79f06f2b8566b8.webm?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/8a08b7c75727f6b77f79f06f2b8566b8.mp4?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be mindful, cubes can be linked together, where action on one impacts all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/12898176109b1f07c5f53f65f103daa7.poster.avif?t=1724771899\" width=500 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/12898176109b1f07c5f53f65f103daa7.webm?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/12898176109b1f07c5f53f65f103daa7.mp4?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>More twists are awaiting in your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/3e9411af3912543942576412161b5657.poster.avif?t=1724771899\" width=500 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/3e9411af3912543942576412161b5657.webm?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/3e9411af3912543942576412161b5657.mp4?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The full game will feature 4 worlds, each comprises of 20 handcrafted levels. Please play the free demo, wishlist and comment!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Cubik</strong> is a minimalist puzzle game revolving around cubes. Each cube can be rotated vertically or horizontally. The goal of the game is to match all cube color with the background.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/0e91e4eee462fa3bb9a314cce51071ef.poster.avif?t=1724771899\" width=500 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/0e91e4eee462fa3bb9a314cce51071ef.webm?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/0e91e4eee462fa3bb9a314cce51071ef.mp4?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When holding the cube, four wings will appear indicating the color of the unseen four faces. When dragging, one wing will appear indicating the color of the upcoming face.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/8a08b7c75727f6b77f79f06f2b8566b8.poster.avif?t=1724771899\" width=500 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/8a08b7c75727f6b77f79f06f2b8566b8.webm?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/8a08b7c75727f6b77f79f06f2b8566b8.mp4?t=1724771899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be mindful, cubes can be linked together, where action on one impacts all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906800/extras/12898176109b1f07c5f53f65f103daa7.poster.avif?t=1724771899\" width=500 height=632 ><sou